  • Classes in com.fortify.util.rest.json.preprocessor.enrich used by com.fortify.util.rest.json.preprocessor.enrich 
    Class and Description
    AbstractJSONMapEnrich
    This abstract implementation for IJSONMapPreProcessor allows for enriching a given JSONMap with additional data.
    JSONMapEnrichWithOnDemandProperty
    This AbstractJSONMapEnrich implementation allows for enriching a given JSONMap instance with on-demand data by adding the configured IJSONMapOnDemandLoader instance to the JSONMap under the configured property name.
    JSONMapEnrichWithOnDemandSpEL
    This JSONMapEnrichWithOnDemandProperty implementation allows for enriching a given JSONMap instance with on-demand data generated through a Spring Expression Language expression.
